{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is a third-person hack-and-slash roguelike game. You will play as a Knight of Light defending against the invasion of the Shadow Empire. Using the power of holy light, you can convert shadow-infected enemies into allies. Try to survive until dawn!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Disclaimer</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot;Blade of Dawn&quot; is a demo we developed in 14 days as part of a game development event. We hope to showcase it on Steam to gather more feedback, which will be very useful for our future game development. We welcome everyone to try it out! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Hack and Survive</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enemies keep coming in the darkness. Slash them freely with multiple skills that let you dominate among crowds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330530/extras/BladeOfDawnGif4.gif?t=1735992661\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Choose Your Upgrade Path</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">After defeating a certain number of enemies, you'll get a chance to upgrade. You can enhance your attributes or gain new traits.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330530/extras/EN_Rogue2.png?t=1735992661\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Convert Your Enemies</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use your ultimate skill (T) to potentially convert enemies into allies. Use this to survive in the sea of enemies!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Controls Instructions</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use WSAD to move, Left-click to attack, QERT to use skills.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Ready To Fight","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3330530/01cf4bc74bfc8a88e4e694829b828a5e5c4ae403.jpg"},{"name":"The Surviver","path":"https://cdn.ak